# Amazon Elastic File System (EFS) Hands-On Lab

## Overview

This lab demonstrates how to create and mount an Amazon Elastic File System shared between EC2 instances.

## AWS Services

- Amazon EC2
- Amazon EFS

---

# Objectives

- Create an EFS File System
- Configure Mount Targets
- Mount EFS on EC2
- Verify shared storage

